{"tid":534152,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"(波鞋撚請入) Vapormax 清潔","createTime":"2018-01-19T13:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T02:06:53.000Z","uid":107697,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0c1f2997ac9de5beecc5d406dd3afef6c1b4c6f4","tid":534152,"uid":107697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:52:43.000Z","msg":"我對triple black老實講其實唔洗點清潔，因為對鞋夠黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但最大問題就係個air底<br />\n行街成日hi花撞到搞到個面有啲花痕<br />\n上網搵左好耐 youtube都冇人講<br />\n自己搵酒精紙巾洗甲水抹都冇用<br />\n成對鞋黑蚊蚊好好睇個底反哂光咁<br />\n就係因為啲刮痕搞到唔好睇<br />\n有冇vapormax用家有我同一樣既苦惱<br />\n你地點搞定冇得搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/215100_6056ce4d899395be71985445f8c86736.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F215100_6056ce4d899395be71985445f8c86736.png&h=34f3f7fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/215101_6056ce4d899395be71985445f8c86736.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F215101_6056ce4d899395be71985445f8c86736.png&h=dce4675a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a58b1853b75731d4bb27d7a0d2ec9b8bc54f1e2e","tid":534152,"uid":7375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T14:00:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97f8c5c5d8925b46ffaf655f63171166609b56b6","tid":534152,"uid":119974,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T14:02:09.000Z","msg":"冇人會留意 唔好咁在意就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdeeabeab671b5336f95d705d13c9ab6b5f40b6f","tid":534152,"uid":57226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T14:03:20.